### Seed Script

#### [MODIFY] [seed.js](file:///Users/raj/Desktop/Client_project/Hospital_Management/database/seed.js)
- Rewrite to use Mongoose models instead of raw MySQL queries
- Same seed data (users, doctors, patients, departments, medicines, beds, etc.)
- Use `mongoose.connect()` instead of `mysql.createConnection()`

---

### Routes (No Changes)
All 11 route files remain **unchanged** — they only define route paths and call controller methods. No database-specific code exists in routes.

### Middleware (No Changes)
Auth middleware and role-check middleware remain **unchanged** — they use JWT, not database queries.

