## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests
1. Run `npm install` to verify mongoose installs correctly
2. Run `node ../database/seed.js` to verify seeding works
3. Start the server with `npm run dev` and test `/api/health` endpoint
4. Test login via `POST /api/auth/login` with seeded credentials

### Manual Verification
- Start the server and verify all API routes respond correctly
- Test full login → dashboard flow from the frontend
